    # OSINT TOOLS #
crt.sh : used to find not yet publically facing domains
haveibeenpwned.com : leaks of account usernames/passwords and email
www.xlek.com : used to search over names, phone numbers, emails, and personal info
spiderfoot.net : crawls the web to find associated domain names, ips, emails, hardware, hostnames, etc... to a domain name
www.shodan.io : finds vulns across a network over the open web. Finds IOT devices that could be exploited
www.network-tools.com : GUI version of enumeration tools
viewdns.info : query's DNS records
